%% Diagram: useSyncExternalStore tearing prevention
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Store
    participant R as React
    participant A as Comp A
    participant B as Comp B

    Note over R: Concurrent render begins (interruptible)
    R->>A: Render
    A->>S: getSnapshot() -> v1
    Note over S: External mutation: v1 -> v2
    R->>B: Render (paused tasks resume)
    B->>S: getSnapshot() -> v2
    Note over R: Pre-commit consistency check<br/>re-read snapshot
    R->>S: getSnapshot() -> v2
    Note over R: v2 != snapshot read by A<br/>Tearing detected
    R->>R: Restart render synchronously with v2
    R->>A: Re-render with v2
    R->>B: Re-render with v2
    R->>R: Commit (all components see v2)
